      <bioghist id="aspace_0a3591eba2e99224289851dff650c956">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>David Martin Hummel received a Bachelor of Science degree from Yale University in 1928. He held various administrative and academic positions at Yale from 1930-1970s.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_bb10862b41fb6a617baa8242a983502e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materails consist of photographic slides of David Hummel documenting Yale science buildings and commencements and a commemorative trip to Elihu Yale's ancestral home in Wrexham, Wales.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
